---
title: Honey-Glazed Halloumi, Chicken & Caesar-Style Salad with Dijon Dressing & Almonds
description: You can put down that supermarket salad because we have one that will truly blow you away with sweetly glazed chicken, halloumi and toasted almonds sprinkled on top. The croutons add a golden crunch while the Dijon mayo dressing wraps everything up with a tasty bow.

